text: Lycée professionnel Pierre Mendès France is a vocational senior high school in Villiers-le-Bel, Val-d'Oise, France, in the Paris metropolitan area. The school is in the north of the Carreaux neighbourhood."Le Lycée Mendès France." Villiers-le-Bel. Retrieved on September 3, 2016.
